## 7. Build & Test Workflows

### 7.1 Prerequisites

This project requires **Bloomberg Clang P2996** (C++26 static reflection).

### 7.2 macOS (local clang or Docker)

```bash
# Detect P2996 support
clang++ -std=c++26 -freflection -x c++ -c /dev/null -o /dev/null 2>/dev/null && echo "P2996_OK" || echo "P2996_MISSING"

# If P2996_OK:
cmake -B build -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=clang++ \
  -DCMAKE_CXX_FLAGS="-std=c++26 -freflection -freflection-latest -stdlib=libc++"
cmake --build build -j$(sysctl -n hw.ncpu)
ctest --test-dir build --output-on-failure
```

### 7.3 Docker (any platform, fallback)

```bash
docker run --rm -v $(pwd):/workspace -w /workspace \
  -e LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/p2996-toolchain/lib/x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu \
  ghcr.io/ximicpp/typelayout-p2996:latest \
  bash -c 'cmake -B build -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=clang++ \
    -DCMAKE_CXX_FLAGS="-std=c++26 -freflection -freflection-latest -stdlib=libc++" && \
  cmake --build build -j$(nproc) && \
  ctest --test-dir build --output-on-failure'
```

### 7.4 Windows (WSL)

```bash
wsl -e bash -c 'cd /mnt/g/workspace/TypeLayout && \
  export CXX=/root/clang-p2996-install/bin/clang++ && \
  export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/root/clang-p2996-install/lib && \
  cmake -B build -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=$CXX \
    -DCMAKE_CXX_FLAGS="-std=c++26 -freflection -freflection-latest -stdlib=libc++" && \
  cmake --build build -j$(nproc) && \
  ctest --test-dir build --output-on-failure'
```

### 7.5 Run a Single Test

```bash
cmake --build build --target test_layout_traits
./build/test_layout_traits
```

### 7.6 Important Notes

- `LD_LIBRARY_PATH` is required at runtime for P2996 libc++.
- All 10 tests must pass (5 core + 5 tools).
- If build fails with stale cache, delete `build/` and reconfigure.
- Git push from Windows uses Windows git (WSL lacks HTTPS credentials).

