## 10. Code Review Checklist

Before committing any change, verify:

- [ ] **Layer correctness**: C++17 tools do NOT include P2996 headers.
- [ ] **consteval vs constexpr**: Signature-generating functions use `consteval`.
- [ ] **FixedString<N> sizing**: N is exact content length, no off-by-one.
- [ ] **Dual-path sync**: If bitmap logic changed, string parser also updated (and vice versa).
- [ ] **Opaque order**: Opaque registrations appear before signature generation.
- [ ] **Virtual inheritance**: Rejected, never silently handled.
- [ ] **Array recursion**: `type_has_opaque` and `compute_has_padding` recurse via `remove_all_extents_t`.
- [ ] **Test coverage**: New functionality has `static_assert` tests.
- [ ] **No .cpp in library**: Only test/ contains `.cpp` files.
- [ ] **No emoji**: Plain text only in all files.
- [ ] **AGENTS.md updated**: Test table reflects any new/changed tests.
- [ ] **All 10 tests pass**: Run full `ctest` before pushing.

